This note documents changes in the local source so that we can incorporate
the lua source code as a library in the gdtk tools.

1. Edit top-level Makefile to:
   + change names of executables: dgd-lua and dgd-luac

2. Add lpeg library to top-level area. Added version: lpeg-1.0.2

3. Edit src/loadlib.c to change environment variables: LUA_PATH, LUA_CPATH

4. Edit src/Makefile to make changes:
   + add lpeg.so target
